scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The Clare Boothe Luce Designated Institution Files contain grant files for designated (also referred to as "invited") institutions. These institutions and universities were selected by Clare Boothe Luce to receive financial support in perpetuity.
